        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100 p-8 flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8 items-center justify-between">
          <div class="max-w-2xl">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-granite mb-2">How we track fresh routes</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4 leading-relaxed">
              Reset timing is based on public posts, gym websites, Instagram stories, and community reports. 
              We aggregate this data to help you find the freshest plastic in Los Angeles.
